data.description: Come one come all this home has it all. This 3 bed 2 bath home features woodwork on the main level and a kitchen with plenty of counter and cabinet space. The basement has a separate entrance, bathroom and cozy living space. Nice wood deck in the back. With easy interstate access and being close to Hanscom Park, it's a great place to live.  AMA
